This lab is intended to get your environment set up for the rest of the labs 
which will follow a similar format.

Hint: there is a helper video/screencast in blackboard.

(1) Download and install:
* java (JDK6 not JRE)
** http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/index.html
* eclipse (IDE for Java EE Developers - the "EE" is important)
** http://eclipse.org/downloads/
* tomcat 7 
** http://tomcat.apache.org/download-70.cgi

(2) Configure eclipse
* configure server
* add egit to eclipse
** http://download.eclipse.org/egit/updates
* clone repository
** git://github.com/amirdt22/CT390.git

(3) checkout/clone lab0
* run project on server (Shift+Alt+X R)
* edit index.jsp and fill it out
* re-run it/refresh your browser and verify your results
* export the project as a war, using the format: lastname-lab0.war (all lowercase)
* submit it on blackboard
